{"word":"Σίμων","slug":"Σίμων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Σίμων, ωνος, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Heb.\">Heb.</a>] <b>Simon<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> S. Peter <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ a.k.a.\">a.k.a.</a> Cephas <b><a href='B:470 4:18'>Mt 4:18</a>; <a href='B:480 1:16'>Mk 1:16</a>; <a href='B:490 4:38'>Lk 4:38</a>; <a href='B:500 1:41'>J 1:41</a>; <a href='B:510 10:5'>Ac 10:5</a>, <a href='B:510 10:32'>32a</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> an apostle <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ a.k.a.\">a.k.a.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Καναναῖος\">Καναναῖος</a></el> <b><el>Μ</el>t 10:4; <el>Μ</el>k 3:18,</b> or (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a></el>) <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ζηλωτής\">ζηλωτής</a></el> <b><a href='B:490 6:15'>Lk 6:15</a>; <a href='B:510 1:13'>Ac 1:13</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b>a brother of Jesus <b><a href='B:470 13:55'>Mt 13:55</a>; <a href='B:480 6:3'>Mk 6:3</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>4.</pp></b> father of Judas Iscariot <b><a href='B:500 6:71'>J 6:71</a>; <a href='B:500 12:4'>12:4</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:500 13:2'>13:2</a>, <a href='B:500 13:26'>26</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>5.</pp></b> a man of Cyrene, bearer of Jesus’ cross <b><a href='B:470 27:32'>Mt 27:32</a>; <a href='B:480 15:21'>Mk 15:21</a>; <a href='B:490 23:26'>Lk 23:26</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>6.</pp></b> a leper <b><a href='B:470 26:6'>Mt 26:6</a>; <a href='B:480 14:3'>Mk 14:3</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>7.</pp></b> a Pharisee <b><a href='B:490 7:40'>Lk 7:40</a>, <a href='B:490 7:43'>43f</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>8.</pp></b> a tanner in Joppa <b><a href='B:510 9:43'>Ac 9:43</a>; <a href='B:510 10:6'>10:6</a>, <a href='B:510 10:17'>17</a>, <a href='B:510 10:32'>32b</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>9.</pp></b> a magician <b><a href='B:510 8:9'>Ac 8:9</a>, <a href='B:510 8:13'>13</a>, <a href='B:510 8:18'>18</a>, <a href='B:510 8:24'>24</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σιμικίνθιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Σινᾶ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}